OL,3,C'Savour every minute': Message from
OL,4,Cdevastated Grandad of Bebe King
OL,6,FThe grandad of a six-year-old girl
OL,7,Fkilled in Southport has expressed his
OL,8,Ffamily's "despair" and urged others to
OL,9,F"savour every minute" they have with
OL,10,Ftheir grandchildren.
OL,12,FFor the first time, Michael Weston
OL,13,FKing has spoken of how the loss of his
OL,14,F"sweet" and "happy" granddaughter Bebe
OL,15,FKing is "impossible to comprehend."
OL,17,FThe musician, who is the father of
OL,18,FBebe's dad, Ben King, revealed that
OL,19,Fher death came as his family gathered
OL,20,Ffor his daughter's wedding, scheduled
OL,21,Ffor the next day.
