OL,3,C'Savour every minute': Message from
OL,4,Cdevastated Grandad of Bebe King
OL,6,FOn an Instagram post he wrote: "As
OL,7,Fmany but not all know, I am taking
OL,8,Fthis moment to confirm that my
OL,9,Fgranddaughter Bebe (the younger
OL,10,Fdaughter of my eldest son) was one of
OL,11,Fthe three girls killed in Southport
OL,12,Flast Monday.
OL,14,F"An act of such consequence, yet so
OL,15,Fpointless, is impossible to comprehend.
OL,17,F"We are bereft but coming together as
OL,18,Fa family, which was already very close-
OL,19,Fknit, to support each other and in
OL,20,Fparticular my son, daughter-in-law and
OL,21,Fmy other granddaughter.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
