OL,3,C'Savour every minute': Message from
OL,4,Cdevastated Grandad of Bebe King
OL,6,F"Bebe was such a sweet, happy little
OL,7,Fthing. Loving life, in particular
OL,8,Fmusic and theatre, and enjoying the
OL,9,Fdeep affection in which she was held
OL,10,Fby her family and friends.
OL,12,F"Monday's events were all the more
OL,13,Fpoignant as we were gathering for my
OL,14,Feldest daughter's wedding, which
OL,15,Fshould have taken place the following
OL,16,Fday - a joyous, beautiful family
OL,17,Foccasion. The shift from joy to
OL,18,Fdespair in a matter of moments is
OL,19,Fprofound."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
