OL,3,C'Savour every minute': Message from
OL,4,Cdevastated Grandad of Bebe King
OL,6,FBebe, Alice Dasilva Aguiar, nine, and
OL,7,FElsie Dot Stancombe, seven, were
OL,8,Ffatally stabbed at a summer holiday
OL,9,Fdance class in the Sefton town on
OL,10,FMonday, 29 July.
OL,12,FEight other children and two adults
OL,13,Fwere seriously injured in the attack,
OL,14,Fincluding the dance class teacher
OL,15,FLeanne Lucas, 35.
OL,17,FMichael thanked his friends and police
OL,18,Fliaison officers for their support at
OL,19,Fthe "saddest and most painful of times"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
