OL,3,C'Savour every minute': Message from
OL,4,Cdevastated Grandad of Bebe King
OL,6,FHe added: "To any of you who have been
OL,7,Fblessed with grand kids, I simply say,
OL,8,Fsavour every minute."
OL,10,FHis message comes as thousands of anti-
OL,11,Fracism protesters gathered in cities
OL,12,Fand towns across the UK in the wake of
OL,13,Fwidespread riots led by the far-right.
OL,15,FThe grandfather added: "I won't
OL,16,Fcomment on what has happened around
OL,17,Fthe country in the aftermath, other
OL,18,Fthan to say peace, love and
OL,19,Funderstanding is what we need, and it
OL,20,Fis all we need. Nothing else."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
