OL,3,C'Savour every minute': Message from
OL,4,Cdevastated Grandad of Bebe King
OL,6,FThe inquests into Bebe, Alice and
OL,7,FElsie's deaths was formally opened at
OL,8,FBootle Town Hall in Merseyside on
OL,9,FWednesday, and adjourned to allow
OL,10,Fcriminal due process to take its
OL,11,Fcourse.
OL,13,FAxel Rudakubana, 17, from Lancashire,
OL,14,Fis set to stand trial next year after
OL,15,Fbeing charged with three counts of
OL,16,Fmurder, 10 counts of attempted murder
OL,17,Fand possession of a bladed article in
OL,18,Fa public place.
